{"tid":921202,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【屯門龍床盤】菁雋展銷廳經紀多過客 首三小時暫收1票","createTime":"2018-11-29T11:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T12:04:11.000Z","uid":174649,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eb433fb15edeb29db82d27afe0292ca8b6b1532f","tid":921202,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181129/large/1543467178_1911.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181129%2Flarge%2F1543467178_1911.jpg&h=6662cb4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「龍床盤」菁雋今日上午11時開始接受認購登記，現場消息指，<strong>首三小時暫收1票</strong>。駐場代理直言，「咁x貴，之前吹200萬內，吹低開高」，嚇窒買家。<br />\n<br />\n以貴絕屯門區登場的「龍床盤」菁雋昨日開價後，今日隨即收票。中午12時許，菁雋設於屯門建豐街悅品酒店的展銷廳，記者現場所見，只有大批地產代理撈客，甚少客人入內了解樓盤資訊。看來就算入票金額僅5萬元，較其他新盤約10萬元少一半，都未能刺激買家入票。<br />\n<br />\n全張價單平均呎價高達1.69萬元，成為屯門史上最貴新盤。首張價單共73伙，售價285萬至928.8萬元，呎價13,452元至22,327元。最平單位為8樓32室，實用面積131方呎，價單價285萬元。"},{"pid":"9155c066630618153403eec6b3148ffdb87b4aae","tid":921202,"uid":147097,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:13:58.000Z","msg":"咁都有一張<br />\n<br />\n算唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f3eabfadbf36c0d747dd6bb0e3d8c658ba1262","tid":921202,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9155c066630618153403eec6b3148ffdb87b4aae","tid":921202,"uid":147097,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:13:58.000Z","msg":"咁都有一張<br />\n<br />\n算唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}